      <div type="book">
        <linkGrp type="notes"/>
        <div n="365-36L-"><head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-365-36L--headnote-1"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-365-36L--headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-365-36L--headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1"><hi rend="underline">Written in the Year</hi> 1724.</l></lg></head><head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-365-36L--headnote-2"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-365-36L--headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-365-36L--headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1"></l></lg></head><head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-365-36L--headnote-3"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-365-36L--headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-365-36L--headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l></lg></head>
      <lg n="1" type="stanza"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-365-36L--line-1"><hi rend="display-initial">D</hi>EAR Sir, I think 'tis doubly hard</l><l/><l n="2" xml:id="spp-365-36L--line-2">Your Ears and Doors shou'd both be barr'd,</l><l/><l n="3" xml:id="spp-365-36L--line-3">Can any thing be more unkind?</l><l/><l n="4" xml:id="spp-365-36L--line-4">Must I not see, 'cause you are blind?</l><l/><l n="5" xml:id="spp-365-36L--line-5">Methinks, a Friend at Night shou'd cheer you:</l><l/><l n="6" xml:id="spp-365-36L--line-6">A Friend that loves to see and hear you:</l><l/><l n="7" xml:id="spp-365-36L--line-7">Why am I robb'd of that Delight?</l><l/><l n="8" xml:id="spp-365-36L--line-8">When you can be no Loser by't.</l><l/><l n="9" xml:id="spp-365-36L--line-9">Nay, when 'tis plain, for what is plainer?</l><l/><l n="10" xml:id="spp-365-36L--line-10">That, if you heard you'd be no Gainer.</l><l/><l n="11" xml:id="spp-365-36L--line-11">For sure you are not yet to learn,</l><l/><l n="12" xml:id="spp-365-36L--line-12">That Hearing is not your Concern.</l><l/><l n="13" xml:id="spp-365-36L--line-13">Then be your Doors no longer barr'd,</l><l/><l n="14" xml:id="spp-365-36L--line-14">Your Business, Sir, is to be heard.</l><l/><l/></lg></div>
      </div>
